ntence\": \"\\\"But it's nothing to a high extreme, it's like the 0.1 of a second.\", \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2741, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2691}, {\"ngram\": \"a high extreme\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2709}, {\"ngram\": \"a second\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just something mentally that you have to deal with, so I am enjoying it and hopefully I can keep doing that this week.\\\"\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2866, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just something\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2761}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A tenth of a second is not an insignificant amount of time, whatever teenager Whittle says, and is enough to leave strategists and sports scientists desperately trying to crack the nut of how best to counter the conditions.\", \"from\": 2868, \"to\": 3091, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A tenth\", \"from\": 2868, \"to\": 2875}, {\"ngram\": \"a second\", \"from\": 2879, \"to\": 2887}, {\"ngram\": \"an insignificant amount\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2918}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2922, \"to\": 2926}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever teenager\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 2945}, {\"ngram\": \"Whittle\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2953}, {\"ngram\": \"strategists\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 2994}, {\"ngram\": \"sports scientists\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3016}, {\"ngram\": \"the nut\", \"from\": 3045, \"to\": 3052}, {\"ngram\": \"the conditions\", \"from\": 3076, \"to\": 3090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it's just about trying to get on people's waves a bit more,\\\" says Anna Hopkin, part of Britain's world record 4x100m mixed relay team in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 3093, \"to\": 3245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3168, \"end\": 3179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Hopkin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anna Hopkin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Hopkin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Hopkin\"}, {\"begin\": 3189, \"end\": 3196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.5506562343720897, \"rank\": 0.816015018841622, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}, {\"begin\": 3239, \"end\": 3244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9473230743497331, \"rank\": 0.055584143563180234, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people's waves\", \"from\": 3135, \"to\": 3149}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 3181, \"to\": 3185}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As soon as you get too far behind someone, the waves are a bit more choppy in here, so it can feel a bit harder if you are a bit too far back.\", \"from\": 3247, \"to\": 3390, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 3282, \"to\": 3289}, {\"ngram\": \"the waves\", \"from\": 3291, \"to\": 3300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So [the tactic is] trying to stay with the pack a bit better.\", \"from\": 3392, \"to\": 3454, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tactic\", \"from\": 3397, \"to\": 3407}, {\"ngram\": \"the pack\", \"from\": 3432, \"to\": 3440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me, going out hard is actually probably better, because I am ahead of the waves and then I can ride the wave coming back.\\\"\", \"from\": 3456, \"to\": 3583, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the waves\", \"from\": 3531, \"to\": 3540}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 3561, \"to\": 3569}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there is a mental challenge as well as a tactical one.\", \"from\": 3585, \"to\": 3643, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a mental challenge\", \"from\": 3598, \"to\": 3616}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Swimmers are conditioned to live and die by the stopwatch, which is spending more time than ever running at these Games.\", \"from\": 3644, \"to\": 3764, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Swimmers\", \"from\": 3644, \"to\": 3652}, {\"ngram\": \"the stopwatch\", \"from\": 3688, \"to\": 3701}, {\"ngram\": \"more time\", \"from\": 3721, \"to\": 3730}, {\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 3752, \"to\": 3763}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In the relay, my split wasn't great in the heat,\\\" adds Hopkin.\", \"from\": 3766, \"to\": 3829, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the relay\", \"from\": 3770, \"to\": 3779}, {\"ngram\": \"my split\", \"from\": 3781, \"to\": 3789}, {\"ngram\": \"the heat\", \"from\": 3806, \"to\": 3814}, {\"ngram\": \"Hopkin\", \"from\": 3822, \"to\": 3828}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I was a bit disheartened after that, but I pulled it back in the final and chopped off quite a lot of time so it's definitely possible to go quick in this pool.\", \"from\": 3831, \"to\": 3995, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"quite a lot\", \"from\": 3922, \"to\": 3933}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3937, \"to\": 3941}, {\"ngram\": \"this pool\", \"from\": 3985, \"to\": 3994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You just have to be a bit more careful with tactics and pacing and try not to take the time to heart as much.\\\"\", \"from\": 3997, \"to\": 4108, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tactics\", \"from\": 4042, \"to\": 4049}, {\"ngram\": \"pacing\", \"from\": 4054, \"to\": 4060}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 4081, \"to\": 4089}, {\"ngram\": \"heart\", \"from\": 4093, \"to\": 4098}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no danger of Richards doing that.\", \"from\": 4110, \"to\": 4152, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no danger\", \"from\": 4119, \"to\": 4128}, {\"ngram\": \"Richards\", \"from\": 4132, \"to\": 4140}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If you have got a lane, you got a chance as far as I am concerned,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 4154, \"to\": 4231, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lane\", \"from\": 4171, \"to\": 4177}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 4187, \"to\": 4195}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not really mind where I am in the pool, as long as I have got water to dive into.\", \"from\": 4232, \"to\": 4319, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 4268, \"to\": 4276}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 4300, \"to\": 4305}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In the nicest possible way, nobody cares what time you go at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 4321, \"to\": 4396, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the nicest possible way\", \"from\": 4325, \"to\": 4348}, {\"ngram\": \"nobody\", \"from\": 4350, \"to\": 4356}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4383, \"to\": 4395}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They care where you finish.\", \"from\": 4397, \"to\": 4424, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And so I am not bothered what times I go here.\", \"from\": 4425, \"to\": 4471, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 4455, \"to\": 4460}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just care about where I finish in finals.\", \"from\": 4472, \"to\": 4515, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 4508, \"to\": 4514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a time and a place to go fast times, and there is a time and place to try and win.\", \"from\": 4517, \"to\": 4609, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 4527, \"to\": 4533}, {\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 4538, \"to\": 4545}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 4577, \"to\": 4583}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 4588, \"to\": 4593}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I think this is the kind of meet, where you want to be doing the winning.\\\"\", \"from\": 4610, \"to\": 4688, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"th